steps:
From the problem, we write the equation \[\frac{1}{2}\cdot\frac{1}{7}\cdot T=\frac{1}{3}\cdot\frac{1}{5}\cdot90.\]Simplifying, we have  \begin{align*}
\frac{1}{14}\cdot T&=\frac{1}{15}\cdot90 \quad \implies \\
